msgstr ""
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8\n"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about managing stress.\n"
"\n"
"We know how stressful it is to bring up teenagers in these times. Learning to manage your stress helps you – and your family."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can managing stress help you and your family? Tap play to find out"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today's topic is managing stress.\n"
"\n"
"It is important to know how to manage our stress. At times our children can behave in ways that make us feel stressed and us as parents can make our children feel stressed too.\n"
"\n"
"So, it is important to notice when we feel stressed and take a pause and breathe. That will help you manage your stress."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"With a few small changes, you can feel more peaceful in your normal day-to-day life.\n"
"\n"
"When you are peaceful, your family members will get calmer too!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_4.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Pause, take a breath. Now hear how taking a simple pause helped @data.characters.media_female_4.name and her teens"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Life is tough sometimes. Before I joined @global.app_name, I used to be grumpy at all times. I would take out my anger on everyone at home, not only my teens but even my husband as well. They would run away when I came home because they knew I would start yelling at them.\n"
"\n"
"Learning to take a pause and breathe was difficult at first. But every time I tried it, it helped me to calm down. Now my teens are no longer running away when I come home and they actually listen better than when I used to shout at them!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s look at an example of how stress can sometimes just get too much, for all of us:"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name lost his job. He was sitting at home feeling frustrated and stressed when @data.characters.f1_son_18.name entered the room."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Leave me alone and mind your own business!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What did I do? You never listen!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I said leave me alone or you will get a beating!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look! I have made a house!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Who cares about your stupid house!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let's think about what happened in this story."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name's
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How do you think @data.characters.f1_father.name's son, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name, felt?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, he did not understand why his father, @data.characters.f1_father.name, got angry, and probably felt all these emotions."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name? should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "And @data.characters.f1_father.name?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sad"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Scared"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Confused"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Angry"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly. @data.characters.f1_father.name was in a difficult situation and this argument only made things worse."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you for thinking along! Let’s go back in time and see what @data.characters.f1_father.name does now:"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.name lost his job. He was sitting at home feeling frustrated and stressed, when his son @data.characters.f1_son_18.name entered the room."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can I have money to buy some airtime?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*(taking a breath)* I’m sorry son. I had a difficult day today. The boss fired me."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Oh no! I need a new school uniform."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name's should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I’ll try, son, and your @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name's job will help us get by while I look for another job."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name? should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Should I also help you look for work, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No it’s okay, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. I appreciate your offer. The most important thing is that you work hard at school. Thanks for listening to me."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s play some soccer together. It will help me get this stress off my mind for a bit."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay, @data.characters.f1_father.role_name!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are a few skills to help you manage stress that you can use with your teens!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "BREATHE"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Breathe slowly. Pause.\n"
"\n"
"Before you say anything, slowly breathe in and out five times. It will calm you, and give you a chance to think."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SHARE"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Share how you feel.\n"
"\n"
"This is hard. Many of us were told not to cry, or show our feelings to our children. But take a deep breath and calmly tell them how you feel. They will understand better, and also learn from you how to deal with stress."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SHOW"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Show them you care.\n"
"\n"
"This is also hard! Stress makes us focus on ourselves. But our teens need our support. Ask them how they feel. Listen to them and comfort them. Try a hug or say \"I understand\". It can change everything."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SEEK"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Seek the positive.\n"
"\n"
"Can you and your teen think about ideas that might help? Can you do something positive together to take your mind off the stress?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Here is your home activity for this week:\n"
"\n"
"Whenever you are feeling stressed or upset with your teen, take five breaths in and out before you react.\n"
"\n"
"And when you're both calm, share with each other how you feel."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Remember to:** \n"
"\n"
"😮‍💨 BREATHE: take five breaths in and out before you react\n"
"🤝🏾 SHARE: when you're both calm, share with your teen how you feel\n"
"💙 SHOW: ask them how they feel to show you care\n"
"🔍 SEEK: find something positive in this situation together"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you respond calmly with your teen this week?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Great! Staying calm will help you and your family."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That’s a good start. When you are stressed, remember to take a few deep breaths, it will make it easier to respond calmly."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I understand, sometimes we just don’t have capacity. Try to keep spending time with your teen - whenever you are ready you can practise responding calmly together."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, when we practice responding calmly and sharing how we feel, our teens learn to do the same. This skill will help them their whole life!"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_1.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how @data.characters.media_daughter_1.name learned to stay calm from her mother"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Whenever I would do something wrong, my mother would get so angry at me and beat me. She would not even listen to me and I would get so angry as well at her and everyone else.\n"
"\n"
"Now, when she gets angry, she first takes a few deep breaths before she responds. It makes everyone calm down instead of causing a big fight.\n"
"\n"
"It really helped me at home and at school. Now, when I feel really angry or stressed, I also take deep breaths like my mother does. I feel like a different person."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done for taking time for yourself today. 🎉"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here is a short video to help you slow down before you go"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When everything feels like it is falling apart And you can't help but raise your voice When all the frustrations are beginning to start Remember that you have a choice\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"You can take pause, you can count to 10 Play a game or do something fun You can phone a friend, someone to confide in Remember you're not the only one\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more\n"
"\n"
"Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Remember all we have to be grateful for Let's slow down Take a few deep breaths Because I really couldn't love you more Because I really couldn't love you more"
msgstr ""
